summary: An ordinance accepting certain additional condemnation awards for the widening and establishing of 25th Avenue Northeast from East 75th Street to Ravenna Avenue, and of Ravenna Avenue from 25th Avenue Northeast to East 82nd Street, under Ordinance 85435, King County Cause No. 501943, and making an appropriation from the Seattle General Arterial Improvement Bond 1954 Fund in connection therewith.
